node.text:
Many of you have asked me how I multitask and organize my days having to play many different roles but also not forgetting ME. lol There actually isn’t really a secret to it. Always wake up early, have a to do list ( a short one is best and gives you more chances to actually tick everything off ), and take your vitamins so you have the energy, mental focus and immunity to do it all. I make sure I always take Multivitamins (Pharmaton Essential) everyday to help me stay healthy to achieve everything I want to do and to boost my immune system during times we are currently living in. Hope you guys enjoy this new vlog " A week in my life" to give you a glimpse of what a week can look like . It varies of course haha. Life is all about balance. #PowerToGiveMore  #PowerKontraSakit

up at 11am on my youtube chanel! 
If symptoms persist, consult your doctor.

node.text:
Who here is a fan of infomercials? lol I remember watching them back in the days and always wanting to call the 1-800 number haha. So I decided to make my own for @EpsonPH. 

Joking aside, this printer is powerful in many ways. Being an artist, I really pay attention to color. With its Ecotank pigment ink, the prints are sharp and guess what? It's water resistant! Furthermore it's heat free technology enables high speed printing with low cost of energy. Best of all, I can do everything from my phone if I'm in a hurry! 
Queue infomercial man voice: Now what are you waiting for! get yours now!  Hehe
I am #TeamEpson @epsonph

node.text:
Because it's been so hot lately, sharing my easy popsicle recipe for Thylane that she loves so much, she didn't even want to share!

It's fun making these snacks for her, and she joins in too. 

These healthy and yummy fruit flavors of @gerberph make it so convenient. Mix with fresh fruit, coconut milk, and yogurt to make the popsicles more exciting and nutritious for your little one.
 
#anythingforbaby #gerberph

node.title: Popsicles are always a good idea!

node.text:
Im not sure how to put this year into a few words. Im sure many of us dont. It's really been many ups and downs, and perhaps one of the best years because of Thylane. Sometimes it is hard to feel happy though because of the many things happening around us. But we need to feel joy and try and find it where we can. I am sure by now many of us have relearned how to find bliss in the smallest and simplest things. And that on its own is amazing. I wish my whole family was here this Christmas, but the faiths have decided otherwise. We are now all healthy and that is the best gifts I could ask for. I love you all so much and miss you guys. Merry Christmas to my loved ones, and to all you amazing human beings. Lets all keep safe, lend a helping hand, and hug again very soon!

thanks @crissbuenviaje for playing! sorry for pics on your face lol. IG aint letting me upload any version but this.

Love my Lenovo Yoga Slim 7i Carbon! I can do so much because it's lightweight so multitasking becomes a piece of cake! 👌 Took a while to get this photo though because a heavy watermelon is never part of the plan, and I might have dropped my laptop more than once but all good! node.text:
Been taking care of my skin lately because Im getting old. Just kidding. Skin care is important for your overall being and health.  So no matter what stage in life you are in, it is important to be kind to yourself and pamper your skin. I have always believed in keeping my routine minimal and using products that work best in giving me brighter and even skin.

Get a chance to win a set of your own Cetaphil Bright Healthy Radiance products by just posting your own radiance routine shelfie and tag @cetaphilbrighthealthyradiance  and hashtag #brightaboutskin #radianceroutine . I will be picking 2 winners!

node.text:
What mornings are made of. There is something quite soothing about baking bread from scratch. 
It takes some time and lots of waiting hours, but nothing beats the smell of a home bakery haha.
After 25 h, and extra 2 at room temp, finally made Tili fresh Brioche bread. And yes, quite pleased with myself haha.
Will post link to recipe on stories if you want to give it a try while at home. 

Song: My Last Teen
Musician: Summer Soul

node.text:
Looking back at those days where we were able to explore the world, go on adventures , meet new people. That's something we'll look forward to in experiencing with Tili.

And speaking of exploring Global, did you know? AIA Philam Life is now AIA Philippines! To guide us better to healthier longer and better lives. 

And looking at that, better days are definitely coming with AIA Philippines understanding global and local to personalize our insurance needs how we would want them making us a part of their one big family. 

Looking forward to better days indeed.
@aiaphilippines  #HealthierLongerBetterLives
